events.name: Quantopian Workshop: Advanced Algorithmic Trading - PAID EVENT
events.description: We would like to invite you to our Quantopian Workshop: Advanced Algorithmic Trading on March 4th. This workshop will walk through the entire quant equity workflow, and will teach you how to develop and deploy your own factor-driven strategy. It will be led by Anthony Ng, who has been teaching investment and portfolio management related modules at educational institutions since 2010. Topics and Exercises Include: - Long-Short Equity Strategies- The Pipeline API- Fundamental Factor Portfolios- Analyzing Factor Performance- Backtesting and Real Market Concerns- Performance Analysis of Backtested Results using Pyfolio This is a paid event - to sign up and for more information, please go to: </a><a href="https://quantopianworkshopsg.splashthat.com/#">https://quantopianworkshopsg.splashthat.com/# For this session, we have set up different ticket levels. We trust you to pick your fair registration rate: - Corporate Rate $699.00: If your company is paying for you to attend, please select the Corporate option.  - Individual Rate $499.00: If you are paying for yourself to attend, please select this rate. - Student Rate $150.00: This rate is only for students and academics.  Please RSVP here.
events.location: The Assemblage, 1 Sophia Road, #02-17. Peace Centre, Singapore 228149
